<h2>Inside GWW</h2>
<ul>
  <li>See <a href="https://www.flickr.com/services/apps/72157622606839772/">screenshots of GWW (including administrative pages) in Flickr's App Garden.</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/dschweisguth/gww/">GWW source code</a> lives on Github.</li>
  <li>GWW is tested on <a href="http://guesswheresf.org:8111/">the JetBrains TeamCity continuous integration server</a>.</li>
  <li><a href="/backups/">Backups of GWW's mysql database</a> live on guesswheresf.org.
    Anyone is welcome to download one for safe keeping or to do their own analysis.
